144
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, to podrazumijeva jedan veliki, veliki,

145
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] velika ulaganja u američku moć. Tu imate jedan poznati dokument,

146
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:05,000
